      "content": "i know i should reach out but it just feels like a lot of effort for nothing. like what's the point of being seen if it's just to be another person struggling in a city full of people? honestly, the idea of just... fading out, where it's just quiet and no one is expecting anything from me anymore... it sounds so much more peaceful than trying to fight to be \"real\" again.",
